Estimate quantile of the list of values Estimation is equivalent to the default quantile estimate in R: if x[j] and x[j+1] are two values adjacent to the quantile, than Q[p] = (gamma - 1) * x[j] + gamma * x[j+1] where gamma = (size - 1) * p + 1 - j and j starts from 1
